GET request format
https://api.petfinder.com/v2/{CATEGORY}/{ACTION}?{parameter_1}={value_1}&{parameter_2}={value_2}

type

breed

size
    small, medium, large, xlarge
        multiple values, e.g. size=large,xlarge.
gender
    male, female, unknown
        gender=male,female
age
    baby, young, adult, senior
        age=baby,senior
color

coat
    short, medium, long, wire, hairless, curly
        coat=wire,curly
status
    adoptable, adopted, found (default: adoptable)

good_with_children
    Can be true, false, 1, or 0
good_with_dogs
    Can be true, false, 1, or 0
good_with_cats
    Can be true, false, 1, or 0
location
    city, state; latitude,longitude; or postal code.
distance
    requires location to be set (default: 100, max: 500)
sort
    recent, -recent, distance, -distance, random (default: recent)
limit
    (default: 20, max: 100)